<br>
They will do anything to belong. They will do anything to be apart. It is our duty as the First and Second Children of darkness to destroy their dreams, and shatter the remains of their worthless souls, for they are unworthy.<br>
<br>
Those pathetic souls who feels pity upon them and allows them to be apart will share the fate of the Third Children and no longer be apart. It is how it is, and it is how it should be.<br>
<br>
But this isn't how it is. Many Dark Guilds allow these Third Children, these unworthy souls, into their halls because they &quot;Act Dark&quot; or they &quot;Are of a Dark Race&quot;.<br>
<br>
A Race, A body is nothing without a Soul. If a Dark God didn't put it there, then it is unclean and unworthy. A perfect dark society would be one that is clenzed of agnosticity, for only the First and Second Children are worthy of the Glory of the Dark. At best, the Third Children are out of Guild slaves. They can toil for the rest of their lives trying to reach what they can never attain in the service of us, if their form doesn't offend us. <br>
<br>
But this isn't how it is, and never will it be this way.<br>
<br>
I throught I'd just inform you of such.<br>
<br>
That is all. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=125476" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.studioeternity.com/EverquestFV/Shinsig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
