<br>
Their are reasons why the Gods put some souls into the bodies they created, and put other souls into bodies created by other gods. The reason may be because that the Children are better in some way then the Followers..<br>
<br>
Or it could be that the Gods just see them differenlty, saying that this soul is suited to be in a body I made, while this other soul is more suited to worship me from another body. Maybe its to spread influence elsewhere, or to mock the gods creation by twisting it to his own will.. who knows. It doesnt nessarily mean the First Children are Better then the Second Children.. just that the First Children came before the Second Children. <p><!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=125476" target="top"><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.studioeternity.com/EverquestFV/Shinsig.jpg"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></a><!--EZCODE LINK END--><br>
