What iss it you ssearch for, what iss it you sseek?   To know who to kill and not to kill?   That iss a judgement call.    You do not wants the responsibility for making ssuch a call on your own?  To take ressposnibility for perhapss killing something inbetween light and darks?  You woulds put thiss burden or responsability upon the shoulderss of the gods themselves?   So you cans kill without havings to think or takes responsibility?    <br>
<br>
Sssuch is the way of a foot soldier, not a knight.   Ifs you sso desire to kill a person because you dont like hiss race, gods or profession, thens admits so.   Do nots try to hides it behinds a god's will, when you are nots a priest...or a true leader......yet. &quot;<br>
